  <summary>10/8/2003--Introduced.
21st Century Job Opportunities Act - Amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to establish a Job Opportunity Grants program of temporary emergency postsecondary education assistance for dislocated workers who have been laid off and who require additional education and training to successfully reenter the workforce. Makes the maximum grant amount equal to the Pell Grant maximum award.</summary>
